---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact Us" description="Get in touch with Entryway Essentials.">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium font-display text-base-900 leading-tight">Contact Us</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-base md:prose-lg prose-base-600 mt-12">
        <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or just want to say hello, feel free to reach out to us. We value your feedback and will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        
        <p>You can contact us via email at:</p>
        <p><strong>contact@entrywayessentials.com</strong></p>

        <p>Or follow us on our social media channels to stay updated with the latest tips and inspiration for your home entryway.</p>
        
        <div class="mt-8">
          <h3>Business Hours</h3>
          <p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
          <p>Saturday - Sunday: Closed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
